════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
                        ESCALATION TRIGGERS
════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
What happens when a timer hits zero.

WHEN YAMATETSU DISCOVERS THE THETA BREACH:
  • Internal investigation → corporate security mobilization
  • Dr. Arisawa designated [DECEASED] or [TRAITOR]
  • Waking Stone recovery becomes priority
  • All Theta personnel (including defectors) become targets

WHEN MORITA DISCOVERS HANA AND REN ARE GONE:
  • Retaliation shifts from professional to personal
  • His network (12 fixers, 8 hitters) mobilized to find them
  • The Georgetown Nexus becomes a hunted location

WHEN THE SPIKER CONTRACT EXPIRES:
  • Krawl's loyalty remains, but patience does not
  • Spikers will seek other contracts unless retained
  • Protection buffer for Puyallup/Ork Underground operations lost

WHEN THE BUNKER IS OPENED WITHOUT ANCHOR:
  • Contents lost or triggered
  • Spikers may be harmed or compromised
  • Intelligence buried forever

